[
  {
    "text": "♪ Mellow instrumental hip-hop music ♪ ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=0"
  },
  {
    "text": "♪ ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=3"
  },
  {
    "text": "Hi, I'm Alex Young, and I'm an engineer ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=10"
  },
  {
    "text": "on the iCloud developer experience team. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=12"
  },
  {
    "text": "CloudKit is an easy way to create great experiences ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=15"
  },
  {
    "text": "by allowing users to effortlessly synchronize data ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=18"
  },
  {
    "text": "between devices. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=21"
  },
  {
    "text": "CloudKit Console helps to make this even easier by providing ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=23"
  },
  {
    "text": "tools that let you work with your app's schema and data. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=26"
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm going to share several updates to CloudKit Console ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=30"
  },
  {
    "text": "that will help you understand and debug ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=33"
  },
  {
    "text": "your application's schema and data. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=35"
  },
  {
    "text": "First, I'll walk through how to use hidden containers, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=38"
  },
  {
    "text": "then dive into a new way you can view records ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=41"
  },
  {
    "text": "using iCloud accounts, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=44"
  },
  {
    "text": "and finally, there are some great updates ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=46"
  },
  {
    "text": "for working with shared zones. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=48"
  },
  {
    "text": "It's common to create lots of containers while in development, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=51"
  },
  {
    "text": "and only focus on a few later on. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=54"
  },
  {
    "text": "You can better organize this ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=56"
  },
  {
    "text": "with the new hidden containers feature. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=57"
  },
  {
    "text": "In CloudKit Console, you can choose ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=60"
  },
  {
    "text": "which containers are hidden or visible. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=62"
  },
  {
    "text": "Hidden containers aren't just hidden ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=65"
  },
  {
    "text": "from the lists inside the Console, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=67"
  },
  {
    "text": "but also across all developer tools, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=69"
  },
  {
    "text": "including Xcode. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=71"
  },
  {
    "text": "Even better, when a container is hidden, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=73"
  },
  {
    "text": "it applies at the team level, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=76"
  },
  {
    "text": "which means all of your test and prototype containers ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=77"
  },
  {
    "text": "no longer clutter your teammates' views. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=80"
  },
  {
    "text": "I'll open the Console and use this new functionality now. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=84"
  },
  {
    "text": "Once you're signed in to the Console, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=88"
  },
  {
    "text": "open the container selector from the top-level navigation. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=90"
  },
  {
    "text": "Then click Manage Containers. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=94"
  },
  {
    "text": "This displays a new menu that allows you to toggle ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=96"
  },
  {
    "text": "the visibility of every container in the current team. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=99"
  },
  {
    "text": "For people with several teams, you can switch between them ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=103"
  },
  {
    "text": "using the account menu in the top right. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=106"
  },
  {
    "text": "Then you can go on to hide containers ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=109"
  },
  {
    "text": "in your other teams as well. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=111"
  },
  {
    "text": "Here's the container from WWDC21, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=114"
  },
  {
    "text": "which isn't needed anymore. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=117"
  },
  {
    "text": "I can hide it, like this. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=119"
  },
  {
    "text": "And if you refresh the container list in Xcode, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=121"
  },
  {
    "text": "you'll see the containers are now hidden there too. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=124"
  },
  {
    "text": "I'll tell you about a new addition to the Console ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=128"
  },
  {
    "text": "that lets you view data as iCloud accounts ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=131"
  },
  {
    "text": "instead of your developer account. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=133"
  },
  {
    "text": "This is called Act As iCloud. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=136"
  },
  {
    "text": "Sometimes, it can be difficult to understand why certain users ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=139"
  },
  {
    "text": "are experiencing trouble with data in their private databases. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=143"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now you have the ability to sign in ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=147"
  },
  {
    "text": "as a separate iCloud account to view private data. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=149"
  },
  {
    "text": "When you're logged in with an iCloud account, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=154"
  },
  {
    "text": "CloudKit Console's query tools work as you'd expect ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=156"
  },
  {
    "text": "from the perspective of that account. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=159"
  },
  {
    "text": "This helps you debug ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=162"
  },
  {
    "text": "development and production issues on behalf of your users. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=163"
  },
  {
    "text": "I'll demonstrate this in the Console ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=167"
  },
  {
    "text": "to illustrate how it works. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=169"
  },
  {
    "text": "This query was performed using my developer account. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=172"
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm going to switch to an iCloud account ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=175"
  },
  {
    "text": "to show how the query results change. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=177"
  },
  {
    "text": "First, navigate to the Act As iCloud account menu item. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=181"
  },
  {
    "text": "This will open a dialog that allows you to sign in ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=185"
  },
  {
    "text": "as an iCloud account. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=187"
  },
  {
    "text": "When I sign in, the context of the Console is going to change. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=189"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now you'll see a banner at the top of the page. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=193"
  },
  {
    "text": "All subsequent operations will be performed ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=195"
  },
  {
    "text": "using the iCloud account instead of your developer account. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=197"
  },
  {
    "text": "You can query records and view zones, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=202"
  },
  {
    "text": "but you cannot perform schema operations. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=204"
  },
  {
    "text": "As you can see, the results of this query ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=208"
  },
  {
    "text": "are for my iCloud account, not my developer account. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=210"
  },
  {
    "text": "Switching to another container or environment ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=214"
  },
  {
    "text": "will stop acting as the iCloud account. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=216"
  },
  {
    "text": "You can also click the button in the banner ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=219"
  },
  {
    "text": "to stop the Act As session. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=221"
  },
  {
    "text": "Remember, acting as an iCloud account applies to records, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=225"
  },
  {
    "text": "not schema, so this feature only works ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=228"
  },
  {
    "text": "in the data parts of the Console. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=230"
  },
  {
    "text": "Attempting to access schema will halt the Act As session. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=233"
  },
  {
    "text": "This feature helps you to better understand ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=237"
  },
  {
    "text": "how your data is used in production ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=239"
  },
  {
    "text": "and investigate data-related bugs more effectively. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=241"
  },
  {
    "text": "Encrypted fields remain unreadable to you ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=246"
  },
  {
    "text": "when acting as another account. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=248"
  },
  {
    "text": "Only the original user who owns the data can decrypt it. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=250"
  },
  {
    "text": "This is by design and helps iCloud ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=254"
  },
  {
    "text": "maintain a high level of security and privacy ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=256"
  },
  {
    "text": "and ensures that sensitive data stays safe. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=259"
  },
  {
    "text": "Next, I'll show you how to share zones in the Console. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=263"
  },
  {
    "text": "CloudKit sharing is a safe way ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=267"
  },
  {
    "text": "to securely share records between users of your app. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=269"
  },
  {
    "text": "This is sharing done securely, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=273"
  },
  {
    "text": "using permissions that allow your app ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=274"
  },
  {
    "text": "to determine a participant's read and write access. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=276"
  },
  {
    "text": "Participant access is further controlled ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=280"
  },
  {
    "text": "by defining shares as public or private. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=282"
  },
  {
    "text": "Zone sharing works by applying rules to every record in a zone. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=287"
  },
  {
    "text": "A shared zone has a CloudKit share record ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=292"
  },
  {
    "text": "that contains the options for accessing each record ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=294"
  },
  {
    "text": "in the zone. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=297"
  },
  {
    "text": "Shared zones cannot have existing shared records. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=299"
  },
  {
    "text": "The standard public and private zone sharing options ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=303"
  },
  {
    "text": "are supported by shared zones. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=306"
  },
  {
    "text": "A public shared zone makes every record visible ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=310"
  },
  {
    "text": "to everyone who has the share code. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=313"
  },
  {
    "text": "Anyone with the short share code can join this share. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=315"
  },
  {
    "text": "This is ideal for records that should be easy to share ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=319"
  },
  {
    "text": "between users without strict access control. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=321"
  },
  {
    "text": "Private shared zones have an additional layer of security ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=325"
  },
  {
    "text": "because members must be in the participant list ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=328"
  },
  {
    "text": "to join the share. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=330"
  },
  {
    "text": "CloudKit Console has several new tools ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=333"
  },
  {
    "text": "for creating and viewing zone shares, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=336"
  },
  {
    "text": "to help you better understand shared zones ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=338"
  },
  {
    "text": "and work with them during development and production. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=340"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's create a zone share now so you can learn how it works. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=343"
  },
  {
    "text": "Navigate to Zones, then select a zone that you want to share. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=348"
  },
  {
    "text": "Click the Configure zone wide sharing... button ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=352"
  },
  {
    "text": "in the details view. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=354"
  },
  {
    "text": "This shows a form that lets you decide ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=356"
  },
  {
    "text": "if you want a public or private share. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=358"
  },
  {
    "text": "Public zones have an additional permission option ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=361"
  },
  {
    "text": "for creating read-only or read/write shares. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=363"
  },
  {
    "text": "For private shares, the permissions are defined ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=367"
  },
  {
    "text": "at a participant level. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=369"
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm going to create a private share, like this.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=371"
  },
  {
    "text": "Once the zone is shared, you will see a short unique ID ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=376"
  },
  {
    "text": "that can be sent to participants to join the share. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=379"
  },
  {
    "text": "Shared zones can be joined in the console ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=383"
  },
  {
    "text": "by using the Accept Shared Record menu option ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=386"
  },
  {
    "text": "found in the Records page. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=388"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now any record created in this zone ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=391"
  },
  {
    "text": "will be automatically shared. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=392"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now that you've seen these updates to CloudKit Console, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=395"
  },
  {
    "text": "go and tidy up your container lists by hiding containers, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=398"
  },
  {
    "text": "try out Act As iCloud so you can see records ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=402"
  },
  {
    "text": "with different iCloud accounts, and try out zone sharing ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=404"
  },
  {
    "text": "for easier sharing of multiple records. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=408"
  },
  {
    "text": "We hope these tools enable you to better understand ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=411"
  },
  {
    "text": "your schema, debug issues in your apps, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-10115/?time=414"
  },
  {
